title: Fortios: HA peer
agents: special
catalog: network/fortigate
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the HA history of a Fortigate firewall cluster.
 It is only available if a cluster has been configured.
 This check issues an error as soon as there is a problem with the Fortigate HA.


 The special agent is required for this check, 
 which can be configured via “FortiOS”.

discovery:
 One service is created.
